AMITY UNIVERSITY
 
Applications are invited for experienced, competent, and committed individuals for the position of Assistant Professor with specialization of Multiple Disability at Amity Institute of Rehabilitation Sciences for its Noida campus:
 
 
Essential Qualification:
 
M.Ed in Specific Disability Area ( Multiple Disability) from a reputed Institute / University with 55%

Having valid RCI registration

Applications invited for Electrical Engineer at APMD - 23-01-2022 - Adv/AUUP/HR/21/126
 Advertisement Date:  23-01-2022                                                                                                                                     Adv/AUUP/HR/21/126

 

AMITY UNIVERSITY
 
We at Amity Power Management Department are looking for experienced, competent and committed individual for the position of Electrical Engineer for its Noida & other Campuses.
 
Desired Qualifications, Skills and experience:
 
At least 4-5 years’ experience in maintenance of HT/LT System including HT/LT Panels, Transformers, Diesel Generating sets, solar generation etc. Should also have knowledge of DISCOM rules & their working system. Incumbent shall be responsible for managing a campus electrically.
 
Knowledge of air-conditioning
 
Candidate must have bachelor’s degree in electrical engineering from recognized institute.
 
Good written and verbal communication skills, sound technical & computer knowledge
 
Age around 30 years
 
Kindly forward your resume within 15 days to skumar10@amity.edu. Please mention “Application for Electrical Engineer” in the subject line
